attachments.title: Would I Why by FFX
attachments.text:
Would I Why is taken from the forthcoming EP "Vodka Something Gin With Whatever" out on Jet Jam, Friday 26th August on iTunes etc.

Watch: <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l8aG8T1Rt5M>
Music video directed by Dan Adlesic, Premiered with Pigeons & Planes

Would I Why Single on Spotify: <http://smarturl.it/11x2sv|smarturl.it/11x2sv>
Would I Why Single on iTunes: <http://smarturl.it/n1uf0p|smarturl.it/n1uf0p>
Would I Why Single on Bandcamp: <http://smarturl.it/lj2rf6|smarturl.it/lj2rf6>

LYRICS 
My home is messy and dusty place
I never clean it up.
It's full of dust it's full of rust,
too gross to find a thing.
But why would i (6x lol)
search for anything?
If I can go to your place
and borrow everything.

I see I like I grab I pack and take it home with me.
Especially if it's your favourite stuff I misplace it carefully.
Now you search in empty home but never find a thing,
well mine is full and locked for you,
cause I got everything.

I see I like I grab I pack and take it home with me, 
especially if it's your favourite stuff 
I misplace it carefully.
